Package dev.nokee.platform.nativebase

Interface TargetMachineAwareComponent

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CApplicationExtension, CLibraryExtension, CppApplicationExtension, CppLibraryExtension, JniLibraryExtension, ObjectiveCApplicationExtension, ObjectiveCLibraryExtension, ObjectiveCppApplicationExtension, ObjectiveCppLibraryExtension, SwiftApplicationExtension, SwiftLibraryExtension
    public interface TargetMachineAwareComponent
    Represents a component that targets multiple target machines.
    Since:
    0.4

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      TargetMachineFactory getMachines()
      Returns a factory to create target machines when configuring getTargetMachines().

    • Method Detail

      • getTargetMachines

        SetProperty<TargetMachine> getTargetMachines()
        Specifies the target machines this component should be built for. The getMachines() property (see TargetMachineFactory) can be used to construct common operating system and architecture combinations.

        For example:

         targetMachines = [machines.linux.x86_64, machines.windows.x86_64]
        Returns:
        a property for configuring the TargetMachine, never null.

      • getMachines

        TargetMachineFactory getMachines()
        Returns a factory to create target machines when configuring getTargetMachines().
        Returns:
        a TargetMachineFactory for creating TargetMachine instance, never null.
